cast.overview: While under the guise of taking his family on a weekend winter getaway, Loid's attempt to make progress on his current mission Operation Strix proves difficult when Anya mistakenly gets involved and triggers events that threaten world peace.
cast.title: SPY x FAMILY CODE: White

details.biography:
Yasuyuki Kase (加瀬 康之, Kase Yasuyuki, March 14, 1971) is a Japanese voice actor from Ōta Ward, Tokyo, who is affiliated with Office Osawa. Previously, he was a member of Mausu Promotion from 1995 to October 31, 2007. He joined Osawa Office on December 1, 2007.

He is known for dubbing the actors Ryan Reynolds, Paul Bettany, Leonardo DiCaprio, Chris Evans, and Josh Stewart.
details.name: Yasuyuki Kase
